 sealed an hundred and forty and four thousand of all the tribes of the children of Israel.","year":96},{"id":"recvMt9wOkcuSZM25","ref":"Rev.7.5","text":"Of the tribe of Juda were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Reuben were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Gad were sealed twelve thousand.","year":96},{"id":"recJypa3xMNDvQF8t","ref":"Rev.7.6","text":"Of the tribe of Aser were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Nepthalim were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Manasses were sealed twelve thousand.","year":96},{"id":"recy6SajIW5bVjcJF","ref":"Rev.7.7","text":"Of the tribe of Simeon were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Levi were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Issachar were sealed twelve thousand.","year":96},{"id":"recbLXTvmsBQgCx1v","ref":"Rev.7.8","text":"Of the tribe of Zabulon were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Joseph were sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Benjamin were sealed twelve thousand.","year":96}]}
